        "created_at": "2024-02-26T16:33:08.202Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I think that cork is fine for laying down for a bit (or longer)\u2026though with the obvious caveat that you might have a nice, dense cork in one bottle and one that loses its seal easily in another (yay, tree bark). But if you have faith that the wine will go for a while, I don\u2019t think the cork will hold it back.</p>",
